    "abstract": "LabOSBench is a lightweight, executable benchmark built on web-based scientific instrument simulators, covering 8 instrument types and 96 subtasks with both subtask-level and end-to-end evaluation. Results show that current agents can complete many structured GUI subtasks, but still struggle with feedback-driven control and long-horizon workflow execution."
